      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced halloumi</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side, or until nicely golden and crisp</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>golden</strong> <strong>halloumi</strong> to kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
