    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, pat dry with kitchen paper, then slice<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into wedges</p><p>Chop your<strong> chives</strong> finely, then peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong>,<strong> Dijon mustard</strong>, <strong>grated garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!) and <strong>chopped chives</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>ranch dip</strong></p>",
